Package: nightwatcher-ingest
Version: 0.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: David Gilinsky <gilinsky@gilinskyresearch.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-astropy, python3-yaml, python3-pymysql, debconf (>= 0.5) | debconf-2.0
Section: science
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/DavidGilinsky/nightwatcher-ingest
Description: Config-driven FITS ingest watcher for astrophotography
 Watches an incoming directory, classifies each FITS frame from its header,
 renames it to a standard, and files it into an organized archive tree.
 .
 Optional extras: stamp frames with a sky-brightness (SQM) reading from a
 NightWatcher database, run configurable external hooks after each file is
 filed, and register as an extension so a NightWatcher2 web-UI tab shows the
 watcher's live activity.
